channel.title: [REQ] Emulous Client [REQ]
channel.description:

I need an Emulous Client, with working head-icons and 377 Gameframe. I am making a project but can't seem to find one anywhere.

Note2: Not really sure where to post it, so I posted it here.
Thanks.
